        <td bgcolor="#CCFF00"><p><font color="#00FF00"><strong><font color="#000099">YFC/Incedo - Call to Prayer</font></strong></font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">We send a text, daily, to all members of YFC/Incedo, at between 12:00 and 12:30pm each day (rationale being that this will be a time when most people are on a break). </font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">1. We pray for 3 minutes<br>
  2. We pray for 3 things </font></p>
          
            <ul>
                <li><font color="#000099">Ourselves</font></li>
                  <li><font color="#000099">One thing in our world (work, relationships, community, country, issue of concern in the wider world)</font></li>
                  <li><font color="#000099">One thing in the mission (May be our choice, may be a specific request).</font></li>
            </ul>            <p><font color="#000086">We start with Praise to God and your kingdom come, your will be done.</font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">3. Three verses to read - from the Book that is the reading for the month. <br>
  (Note: These may be read at the time or referred to later depending on circumstances of each individual at the time).</font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">Key things; we are bedding in a discipline; we are all doing it together at the same time.</font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">We call it 3x3x3.</font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">We will start 3/3/07 and run for three months (till the gathering) and then evaluate it. </font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099"> To send out to all members will cost (on current numbers) around $2,000 per year. Each Text to an individual will cost 12c per day (including GST) which equates to $43.80 per year.</font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">We are inviting members to make a voluntary donation of $40.00 per year to cover the costs. </font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">Glen Bennett will manage it along with the Prayer update. Mike Wood will select the bible verses for each day. </font></p>
          <p><font color="#000099">We may expand to include associates and helpers at a later date.</font></p></td>
